comment.narrative:
Six (6) GYW/CSOs namely; Polycom, Girl Up Initiative, Network for Adolescent and Youth of Africa, Gender and Media Initiative Trust, Network of Ethiopian Women Association, Yellow Movement Ethiopia and Girl Up Initiative Ethiopia  were supported by HoAYN to participate in various regional advocacy spaces such as: 38th GIMAC Summit (Pre-AU Summit) in Addis Ababa, Ethiopia, 8th Session of the ARFSD in Kigali -Virtually, 66th CSW, One Million Next Level Validation Meeting organized by AU and the 20th Sitting of the Civil Society Organizations Forum on the African Charter on the Rights and Welfare of the Child where their voices was recognized. 
Note: the extra 5 CSOs were supported to participate virtually. 
Finance: over expenditure in this budget line was due to high cost of air tickets;

